abstract: Fortune Bank, a Seattle commercial bank, said Thursday it is planning to raise about $360 million in an initial public offering.
snippet: Fortune Bank, a Seattle commercial bank, said Thursday it is planning to raise about $360 million in an initial public offering.
lead_paragraph: Fortune Bank, a Seattle commercial bank, said Thursday it is planning to raise as much as $460 million in an initial public offering.

headline.main: Seattle’s Fortune Bank Plans $360 Million I.P.O.
